It includes your topic sentence and all the support sentences you wrote based on your idea web.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"ju-powertip\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Remember!</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>When you write, you should always plan to go back over what you have written to revise and edit.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p>","rightText":"<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"ju-tableplain ju-tight\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Body paragraph 1:</strong></p><p>When I decide to spend a few hours seeing a movie in a theater, I know that I am leaving many distractions and interruptions at home.&nbsp; While my eyes are glued to the big screen, I am not able to open my computer and check work email, even for a minute.&nbsp; There is no way I can take care of housework or jobs around the house.&nbsp; The size of the screen and placement of stadium seating provide a visual experience that cannot be created on TV at home.&nbsp; The surround sound experience makes the dialogue, music, and sound effects come alive for the audience.&nbsp; Finally, new techniques allow the viewer to be immersed in the movie, truly bringing you to places you have never been.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"settings":{"showAudio":1,"showNext":1,"showHeader":1,"hideRightPanel":0,"delayStep":0,"delayRight":0,"showRuler":0,"showRFB":1},"leftText":"<p>Review your thesis statement and your writing web to plan the third body paragraph of your contest essay.<br />&nbsp;</p>","rightText":"<p><img alt=\"The part of the writing web for your third body paragraph.
